newpage Legend and Notes

note over App, Remote
  **STEM Communication Protocol - Sequence Diagram Legend**
  ====
  
  **Layer Colors**
  ----
  • Green (#E0F2F1) - Application Domain (Layer 7)
  • Yellow (#FFF8E1) - Security Domain (Layer 6)
  • Indigo (#E8EAF6) - Session Domain (Layer 5)
  • Red (#FFEBEE) - Transport Domain (Layer 4)
  • Purple (#F3E5F5) - Routing Domain (Layer 3)
  • Orange (#FFF3E0) - Framing Domain (Layer 2)
  • Blue (#E3F2FD) - Physical Domain (Layer 1)
  
  **Message Types**
  ----
  ? Synchronous call
  ?- Return/Response
  ->> Asynchronous event
  
  **Key Constants**
  ----
  • Max Chunk Size: 200 bytes
  • Packet ID Range: 1-7 (rolling)
  • Session Timeout: 600 seconds (default)
  • Heartbeat Interval: 2 seconds
  • Max Hops: 5 (default)
  • CRC: CRC-16
  • Encryption: AES-128 ECB with PKCS7 padding
  
  **LayerResult States**
  ----
  • Success - Operation completed successfully
  • Error - Operation failed with error message
  • Incomplete - Waiting for more data (e.g., chunk reassembly)
  • Skipped - Data passed through unchanged (e.g., duplicate broadcast)
end note

@enduml
